Instead of all that code you've got, I'd try:


```
game.spawn = false
game.spawncount = 0
game.count2 = 0
game.changedcount2 => {
  switch(game.count2){
    case(1,2,3){
      game.spawn = false
    }
    case(4){
      game.count2 = 0
    }
  }
}
```

